nodes.text: Vivienne Chandler (November 6, 1947 - June 6, 2013) was an actress and photographer. She became a photographer after retiring from acting and was a Fellow of the Royal Photographic Society. Though her scene was cut, Chandler portrayed Dorovio Bold during the Battle of Endor. Her scene was not included in the Blu-Ray release of the film. She died June 6, 2013.
